# cterest sample

Markdown fixture served by the mock API.

## Features

- **Bold** and _italic_ text
- Inline `code` and a [link](https://example.com)
- A fenced block:

```ts
const answer: number = 42
```

> Edit me in the app and hit save — this file is overwritten on disk.

